org.apache.gravitino.client

Class GravitinoAdminClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.gravitino.client.GravitinoClientBase
      • org.apache.gravitino.client.GravitinoAdminClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, SupportsMetalakes

    public class GravitinoAdminClient
extends GravitinoClientBase
implements SupportsMetalakes
    Apache Gravitino Client for the administrator to interact with the Gravitino API, allowing the client to list, load, create, and alter Metalakes.

    Normal users should use GravitinoClient to connect with the Gravitino server.
